297.body: Creates a new auction. Creating a reserve auction does not start it. Auctions are started once a bid of the reserve price or higher is placed. function createReserveAuction(MetadataBundle[2] calldata _bundles, Signature[2] calldata _signatures, address _currencyAddress, uint256 _reservePrice) external bundlesAuthorized(_bundles, _signatures) onlySonaAdminOrApprovedTokenOperator(_bundles[0].tokenId) onlySonaAdminOrApprovedTokenOperator(_bundles[1].tokenId); Parameters Name Type Description _bundles MetadataBundle[2] _signatures Signature[2] _currencyAddress address The address of the currency bids will be in. _reservePrice uint256 The reserve price of the auction.
297.title: createReserveAuction

337.body: the constructor-like function used for proxy contracts Pass in either a non-zero paymentToken_ or wETHToken_ param. One and only one should be non-zero function initialize(address _eoaAdmin, IERC721 sonaRewardToken_, IERC20 paymentToken_, IWETH wETHToken_, address rewardVault_, string calldata claimLookupUrl_) public initializer; Parameters Name Type Description _eoaAdmin address The administrator of proxy upgrades and RewardRoots sonaRewardToken_ IERC721 The address of the SonaRewardToken NFT smart contract paymentToken_ IERC20 The address of the reward token Collectors and Artists earn wETHToken_ IWETH The address of the wETH token if Collectors and Artists earn ETH rewardVault_ address The holder of the reward token that has granted this contract enough of an allowance to operate claimLookupUrl_ string The templated url returned via OffchainLookup. Must be EIP-3668 compliant
337.title: initialize
